Hawaiian Burger

25 min
$12.99
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinGluten-Free Option Available

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Quick MealSummer BBQComfort Food

Description

A juicy beef patty topped with sweet grilled pineapple and savory teriyaki sauce, served on a soft bun for a taste of the tropics.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • pineapple rings: 4
  • hamburger buns: 4
  • teriyaki sauce: 1/2 cup
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • lettuce: 4 leaves
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
